      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home. This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one, and it looks just as gorgeous as it did on the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection inside and out. It drives like a total dream and is ready for your next big adventure! Come swing by and take a look; I promise you won't be disappointed!",
